headline: Mayors in the Carolinas, Tennessee proclaim Dec. 12 'Share the Warmth Day'
summary: In the spirit of giving and to encourage sharing warmth with neighbors, the mayors of Charlotte, Fayetteville, Greensboro and Wilmington, N.C.; Greenville, S.C.; and Nashville, Tenn., have proclaimed Dec. 12, 2024, as "Share the Warmth Day" in their respective cities.
